{
  "id": "poetry-note",
  "name": "诗歌便签",
  "category": "poetry",
  "description": "一张诗歌风格的便签，带有诗意和文学气息",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "random",
    "probability": 0.02,
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "mood",
        "operator": "contains",
        "value": "诗意|浪漫|文艺|抒情|感伤",
        "description": "诗意或浪漫场景可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "poemTitle": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "诗歌标题"
    },
    "poemContent": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 300,
      "description": "诗歌内容"
    },
    "author": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "作者"
    },
    "date": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "日期"
    },
    "mood": {
      "type": "string",
      "default": "抒情",
      "options": ["抒情", "浪漫", "感伤", "哲理", "自然"],
      "description": "诗歌情绪"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一首诗歌。\n\n背景信息：\n- 作者：{{author}}\n- 情绪：{{mood}}\n- 场景：{{scene}}\n\n要求：\n1. 使用诗歌风格的语言\n2. 内容要富有诗意和情感\n3. 可以是现代诗或古典诗风格\n4. 字数控制在100-200字之间\n\n请直接输出诗歌内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "poetry",
    "colors": ["#f5f5f5", "#e8e8e8", "#c41e3a"],
    "mood": "诗意浪漫"
  },
  "rarity": "rare",
  "collectible": true
}